'''2013年洛杉磯國際機場槍擊案'''是在2013年11月1日[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]上午約9:20，發生在[[洛杉磯國際機場|洛杉磯國際機場]]第三航廈的槍擊案件，年齡23歲的保罗·安东尼·希恩西亚（Paul Anthony Ciancia）被控以[[來福槍|來福槍]]射殺了一名[[美國聯邦政府|美國聯邦]]{{link-en|美国运输安全委员会|Transportation Security Administration|运输安全委员会}}的官員，另外有多人受傷<ref>{{cite news
 |title= 洛杉矶机场枪击案嫌犯或因被辞退报复社会
 |url= http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2013/11-03/5456653.shtml
 |work= 京华时报
 |publisher= 中國新聞網
 |date= 2013-11-03
 |accessdate= 2013-11-09
 |archive-date= 2016-03-05
 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305083905/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2013/11-03/5456653.shtml
 |dead-url= no
 }}</ref>。

==過程==
在2013年11月1日上午，希恩西亚據稱進入[[洛杉磯國際機場|洛杉磯國際機場]]第三航廈，從袋子中拿出一把半自動<ref name=M&P-15>{{cite web|title=S&W M&P-15 Product Website|url=http://www.smith-wesson.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/Category4_750001_750051_757785_-1_757784_757784_image|accessdate=November 3, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106083342/http://www.smith-wesson.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/Category4_750001_750051_757785_-1_757784_757784_image|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[史密斯威森軍警型M&P15半自動步槍|史密斯威森軍警型M&P15]][[來福槍|來福槍]]，隨即開槍<ref name=deadly/>。接著進入美国运输安全委员会的掃描區域，通過{{link-en|安全檢查點|Security checkpoint}}，進入安全區內。一名證人在接受CNN訪問時說道，嫌犯在開槍時並非在奔跑，而是慢慢走進中央大厅。希恩西亚在航廈的[[美食廣場|美食廣場]]遇到{{link-en|洛杉磯機場警局|Los Angeles Airport Police}}的警員，展開槍戰。希恩西亚身中四槍後被捕，由救護車送到附近的醫院急救<ref>{{cite news|title=Shooter opens fire at Los Angeles International Airport|url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/11/01/21277650-shooter-opens-fire-at-los-angeles-international-airport?lite|accessdate=November 1, 2013|date=November 1, 2013|agency=NBC News|archive-date=2017-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714200544/http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/11/01/21277650-shooter-opens-fire-at-los-angeles-international-airport?lite|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==傷亡==
===死者===
希恩西亚在機場射殺了{{link-en|美国运输安全委员会|Transportation Security Administration|运输安全委员会}}的官員Gerardo I. Hernandez。Hernandez年鹷39歲，在送達{{link-en|洛杉矶加州大学雷根医院|Ronald Reagan UCLA Medical Center}}後宣告死亡<ref>{{cite web|title=LAX shooting: Slain TSA agent identified as Gerardo I. Hernandez|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-lax-shooting-slain-tsa-agent-identified-as-gerardo-i-hernandez-20131101,0,4620544.story?track=rss#axzz2jQAO3Gla|publisher=LA Times|accessdate=November 2, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106030952/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-lax-shooting-slain-tsa-agent-identified-as-gerardo-i-hernandez-20131101,0,4620544.story?track=rss#axzz2jQAO3Gla|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=TSA Agent Killed, 6 Injured In LAX Shooting|url=http://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2013/11/01/lapd-incident-reported-in-terminal-3-at-lax/|publisher=losangeles.cbslocal.com|accessdate=November 2, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102030642/http://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2013/11/01/lapd-incident-reported-in-terminal-3-at-lax/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他是十二年來，首位在執勤中死亡的运输安全委员会官員<ref>{{cite web|title=Shooting at Los Angeles airport|url=http://www.washinhttp://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/03/us/los-angeles-airport-partly-closed-after-shooting.html?hpgtonpost.com/blogs/liveblog-live/liveblog/shooting-at-los-angeles-airport/#b6d7b366-da2d-4517-98a4-05dc5cd8bc15|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=November 1, 2013}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Maritnez, Michael|title=Suspect shot, in custody at LAX after TSA agent killed|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/11/01/us/lax-gunfire/index.html?hpt=hp_t1|publisher=CNN|date=November 1, 2013|accessdate=November 1, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101232255/http://www.cnn.com/2013/11/01/us/lax-gunfire/index.html?hpt=hp_t1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Hernandez是一位行為偵測專家，在15歲時由[[薩爾瓦多|薩爾瓦多]]移民到美國<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-1103-lax-shooting-20131103,0,7342159.story#axzz2jmqKVQgo|title=Suspected LAX gunman had his targets clearly in mind|publisher=Los Angeles Times|date=2013-11-03|accessdate=2013-11-05|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104213951/http://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-1103-lax-shooting-20131103,0,7342159.story#axzz2jmqKVQgo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===傷者===
七名傷者在現場接受治療。受到槍擊的包括另一位运输安全委员会的成員及一名29歲的男性<ref>{{cite web|author=Abdollah, Tami|title=LAX suspect remains heavily sedated, under guard|url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/crime/article/LAX-suspect-remains-heavily-sedated-under-guard-4952346.php#photo-5412713|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=November 4, 2013|accessdate=November 4, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104214846/http://www.sfgate.com/news/crime/article/LAX-suspect-remains-heavily-sedated-under-guard-4952346.php#photo-5412713|dead-url=no}}</ref>。六名傷者送到附近的地區醫院，而二位有槍傷的傷者送到洛杉矶加州大学雷根医院。有些傷者不是受到槍傷<ref>{{cite web|title=6 Hospitalized After LAX Shooting; Suspect in Custody|url=http://marinadelrey.patch.com/groups/police-and-fire/p/shots-fired-at-lax-tsa-employee-wounded|publisher=marinadelrey.patch.com|accessdate=November 1, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106061106/http://marinadelrey.patch.com/groups/police-and-fire/p/shots-fired-at-lax-tsa-employee-wounded|archive-date=2013-11-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

希恩西亚在第三航廈美食廣場遭遇執法部門，當時已在緊急狀態下，希恩西亚身中四槍<ref>{{cite web|title=LAX gunman Paul Ciancia pictured with bullet wound to the face|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/pictured-lax-gunman-shot-face-article-1.1504943#ixzz2jX6LHheh|publisher=NY Daily News|accessdate=November 2, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103220001/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/pictured-lax-gunman-shot-face-article-1.1504943#ixzz2jX6LHheh|dead-url=no}}</ref>，警員將希恩西亚手上的來福槍踢落<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-lax-shooting-eyewitness-20131101,0,1026875.story|title=LAX shooter was 'calm, pacing, scanning the crowd' during rampage|accessdate=2013-11-10|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103203807/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-lax-shooting-eyewitness-20131101,0,1026875.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>．隨後由救護車送到地區醫院處理。KCAL-TV拍到的影片中，希恩西亚由救護車送到醫院，周圍有多名警員，希恩西亚被[[手銬|手銬]]銬在擔架上<ref>{{cite news|title=LAX shooting: At least 3 shot; gunman in custody|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-live-lax-shooting-tsa-agent-alleged-gunman-shot-20131101,0,3517669.story#axzz2jPyVqqIV|accessdate=November 1, 2013|newspaper=LA Times|date=November 1, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102045519/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-live-lax-shooting-tsa-agent-alleged-gunman-shot-20131101,0,3517669.story#axzz2jPyVqqIV|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Police: Suspect in custody; TSA agent shot, killed at LAX shooting|url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2013/11/01/Reports-Suspect-dies-TSA-agent-shot-killed-at-LAX-shooting/UPI-80811383326473/?spt=rln&or=2|accessdate=November 1, 2013|newspaper=UPI.com|date=November 1, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101194648/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2013/11/01/Reports-Suspect-dies-TSA-agent-shot-killed-at-LAX-shooting/UPI-80811383326473/?spt=rln&or=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==嫌犯==
嫌犯只有一人，是住在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]年齢23歲的保罗·安东尼·希恩西亚（Paul Anthony Ciancia）<ref>{{cite web|title=Police: Suspected LAX gunman, 23, identified and in custody; 3 wounded|url=http://www.kens5.com/news/Los-Angeles-International-Airport-evacuated-after-shots-reportedly-fired-230222821.html|publisher=KENS TV|accessdate=November 1, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104020132/http://www.kens5.com/news/Los-Angeles-International-Airport-evacuated-after-shots-reportedly-fired-230222821.html|archivedate=2013年11月4日}}</ref>。希恩西亚在[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[塞勒姆縣|塞勒姆縣]]的Pennsville長大<ref>{{cite web|title=LAX Shooter Paul Anthony Ciancia’s Personal Details Emerge|url=http://www.mediaite.com/online/lax-shooter-paul-anthony-ciancias-personal-details-emerge/|publisher=Mediaite|accessdate=November 1, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103084234/http://www.mediaite.com/online/lax-shooter-paul-anthony-ciancias-personal-details-emerge/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2008年時從Salesianum學校畢業<ref>{{cite news|author=Rubinkam, Michael; Matheson, Kathy|title=NJ police: Dad called, worried about LAX suspect|url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/crime/article/NJ-police-Dad-called-worried-about-LAX-suspect-4947599.php|agency=Associated Press|date=November 1, 2013|accessdate=November 1, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104014913/http://www.sfgate.com/news/crime/article/NJ-police-Dad-called-worried-about-LAX-suspect-4947599.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。希恩西亚帶了一張紙條，上面寫他「想要殺TSA（美国运输安全委员会）」並且稱他們是豬。11月1日稍早時，希恩西亚的家人因為多次試圖聯絡他卻都失踪，因此申請失踪人口報告，[[洛杉矶警察局|洛杉矶警察局]]去他的住所時，希恩西亚恰巧不在住處中，他的室友說他當天稍早時還在住處。因為警員已確認希恩西亚在哪裡，因此沒有提出失踪人口報告。希恩西亚在幾天前才提到他的生活<ref>{{cite web|title=LAX Shooting Suspect from South Jersey: Police|url=http://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/local/LAX-Shooting-Suspect-New-Jersey-Paul-Ciancia-Pennsville-230258861.html?_osource=SocialFlowTwt_NYBrand|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=2013-11-10|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104030302/http://www.nbcnewyork.com/news/local/LAX-Shooting-Suspect-New-Jersey-Paul-Ciancia-Pennsville-230258861.html?_osource=SocialFlowTwt_NYBrand|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==最初的反應==
洛杉機機場警局疏散了許多航厦的乘客，並尋找是否有其他的嫌犯。荷槍實彈的警員在車內巡邏，並由[[警犬|警犬]]找尋機場附近，和機場以行人天橋相連的停車場，看是否有爆裂物。[[美國聯邦航空總署|美國聯邦航空總署]]使所有要起飛的所有航班停飛，跑道24L及24R及第1,2,3航厦也關閉，約三百名乘客被疏散到Tom Bradley國際航厦，並在離開航厦時重新進行掃描檢查<ref>{{cite web|title=Gunman opens fire at LAX, killing TSA worker and wounding others|url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/11/01/21277650-gunman-opens-fire-at-lax-killing-tsa-worker-and-wounding-others?lite|publisher=NBC News|accessdate=November 1, 2013|archive-date=2013-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101233727/http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/11/01/21277650-gunman-opens-fire-at-lax-killing-tsa-worker-and-wounding-others?lite|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有些班機被調整到[[大洛杉矶地区|大洛杉矶地区]]的其他機場，大部份改到[[洛杉磯安大略國際機場|洛杉磯安大略國際機場]]，有些則到[[長灘機場|長灘機場]]。大部份調整的班機都是預定在1,2,3航厦起飛的航班<ref>{{cite web|title=Some flights diverted to ONT after LAX shooting|url=http://www.pe.com/local-news/local-news-headlines/20131101-some-flights-diverted-to-ont-after-lax-shooting.ece|publisher=pe.com|accessdate=November 1, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102211206/http://www.pe.com/local-news/local-news-headlines/20131101-some-flights-diverted-to-ont-after-lax-shooting.ece|archivedate=2013年11月2日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.presstelegram.com/general-news/20131101/long-beach-airport-responds-to-incident-at-lax | title=Long Beach airport responds to incident at LAX | work=Press-Telegram | date=November 1, 2013 | accessdate=November 1, 2013 | author=Marquez, Liset | location=Long Beach, California | archive-date=2013-11-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103134243/http://www.presstelegram.com/general-news/20131101/long-beach-airport-responds-to-incident-at-lax | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==起訴==
聯邦檢查官在11月2日以謀殺聯邦官員及在國際機場使用暴力的罪名對希恩西亞起訴，由於還有二個人受到槍傷，希恩西亞還可能因為試圖謀殺的罪名受到州政府或聯邦政府的起訴<ref>{{cite news|title=SUSPECTED LAX GUNMAN CHARGED|url=http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_LAX_SHOOTING?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2013-11-02-19-27-28|work=Associated Press|accessdate=November 2, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104082208/http://hosted.ap.org/dynamic/stories/U/US_LAX_SHOOTING?SITE=AP&SECTION=HOME&TEMPLATE=DEFAULT&CTIME=2013-11-02-19-27-28|archivedate=2013-11-04}}</ref>。

